542
00:59:52,968 --> 00:59:54,052
Aku ulang lagi.

543
00:59:54,928 --> 00:59:56,096
Sebutkan namamu.

544
00:59:58,056 --> 00:59:59,307
Sebutkan!

545
01:00:23,957 --> 01:00:24,958
Baik.

546
01:00:26,668 --> 01:00:28,837
